    "---\n",
    "## 4. TF-IDF Vectorisation\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\text{TF-IDF}(t,d) = \\underbrace{\\log(1+f_{t,d})}_{\\text{sublinear TF}} \\times \\underbrace{\\log\\frac{N}{df_t}}_{\\text{IDF}}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "| Parameter | Value | Rationale |\n",
    "|---|---|---|\n",
    "| `ngram_range=(1,2)` | unigrams + bigrams | Captures `machine learning`, `data pipeline` as single features |\n",
    "| `max_features=8000` | vocabulary cap | Efficient for 500-job corpus |\n",
    "| `sublinear_tf=True` | TF = log(1+tf) | Prevents long descriptions from dominating |"
   ]
  },

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "s4",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "from sklearn.feature_extraction.text import TfidfVectorizer\n",
    "\n",
    "JOBS = df.to_dict('records')\n",
    "corpora = [build_job_corpus(job) for job in JOBS]\n",
    "\n",
    "vectorizer = TfidfVectorizer(ngram_range=(1,2), max_features=8000, sublinear_tf=True)\n",
    "tfidf_matrix = vectorizer.fit_transform(corpora)\n",
    "feature_names = vectorizer.get_feature_names_out()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f'TF-IDF matrix:')\n",
    "print(f'  Shape    : {tfidf_matrix.shape[0]} jobs x {tfidf_matrix.shape[1]:,} features')\n",
    "print(f'  Sparsity : {1 - tfidf_matrix.nnz/(tfidf_matrix.shape[0]*tfidf_matrix.shape[1]):.1%}')\n",
    "print(f'  NNZ      : {tfidf_matrix.nnz:,}')\n",
    "\n",
    "v0 = tfidf_matrix[0].toarray().flatten()\n",
    "top_idx = np.argsort(v0)[::-1][:15]\n",
    "print(f\"\\nTop TF-IDF terms for '{JOBS[0]['title']}'  :\")\n",
    "for i in top_idx:\n",
    "    print(f'  {feature_names[i]:<30} {v0[i]:.4f}')"
   ]
  },

