    "\n",
    "Displayed as a radar chart on `/recommendations` for each job card.\n",
    "\n",
    "| Axis | Range | Formula | Notes |\n",
    "|---|---|---|---|\n",
    "| `skills_match` | 0-100 | `matched / total_job_skills * 100` | Partial substring match both directions |\n",
    "| `role_alignment` | 40-99 | `cosine * 220`, clamped | Per-pair TF-IDF cosine |\n",
    "| `salary_fit` | 20-100 | `midpoint / $200k * 100` | Missing salary = 50 (neutral) |\n",
    "| `seniority` | 20-100 | `100 - abs(yoe - required) * 12` | Required YOE from title keywords |\n",
    "| `demand_score` | 70-95 | Static `DEPT_DEMAND[dept]` | Market heat signal |"
