    "$$P@K = \\frac{|\\{\\text{relevant in top-}K\\}|}{K}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "Relevance: result is relevant if `dept` or `title` contains a domain keyword for the user's background. This is a proxy metric — real-world precision would use implicit feedback (clicks, applications, dwell time)."
